<hr />
<line>Gregory:
<textEffects>(What exactly was he doing in Mr. Dover's room...? And moreover... something is odd about his semifinal entry. A pastry chef bad at design, and a sculptor skilled only at designing... It would have been extremely difficult for either of them to win the contest alone. Could it be that Mr. Gustavia and Mr. Dover's connection is...)</textEffects> Detective Badd. We have reason to suspect the actions of Dane Gustavia.
</line><line>Badd:
Yeah...
</line><line>Gregory:
