</line><line>Courtney:
Really? I wonder about that. Overturning a verdict of the Goddess of Law... is much harder than you think.
</line><line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(Is the P.I.C. trying to justify the verdict from 18 years ago...!?)</textEffects>
</line><line>Gustavia:
Nwahahahahahahaha! How unfortunate, Sir Prosecutor!
</line><line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(...Is there nothing I can do!? Is there no way to continue pursuing Mr. Gustavia!?)</textEffects>
</line>
